a97d11151162da16fc32dccdc23a540a9660d08c.name: searchPlace
a97d11151162da16fc32dccdc23a540a9660d08c.source:
query searchPlace($title: String!, $category: String, $lastID: Int) {
  searchPlace(title: $title, category: $category, lastId: $lastID) {
    __typename
    id
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    title
    address
    zipCode
    x
    y
    category
  }
}

5953e24e4d902cc3bbad8b873596e07e97b80992.name: searchReview
5953e24e4d902cc3bbad8b873596e07e97b80992.source:
query searchReview($title: String, $category: String, $lastID: Int) {
  searchReview(title: $title, category: $category, lastId: $lastID) {
    __typename
    id
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    title
    content
    upload
    userId
    placeId
    comments {
      __typename
      id
      createdAt
      updatedAt
      payload
      reviewId
    }
  }
}

82fedfbfbf51c5b207939d62c9cc80766e7d08d6.name: seeProfile
82fedfbfbf51c5b207939d62c9cc80766e7d08d6.source:
query seeProfile($userName: String!) {
  seeProfile(userName: $userName) {
    __typename
    id
    userName
    nickName
    email
    avatar
    bio
    gender
    ageRanger
    createdAt
    updatedAt
    platformType
  }
}
